<h1 style="text-align: center;">.....Corporate mission/mission experience life, to create the future.....</h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';">ZONG YIH officially established in 1978, is one of the leading manufacturers of custom molded rubber parts in Taiwan, and it began by serving the wide variety of industries and manufacturers that make up the industrial heartland of Taiwan, afterward, extend exportation to over 20 countries world-wide, furthermore, we are ISO 9001 certified company and fully integrated with capabilities from material and tool development through full production.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';">We have over 130 employees and 47 sets of production equipment including&nbsp;500-ton and 1000-ton large platen compression and injection molding machines. ZONG YIH covers most of the applications in all industries with our wide range of products including sealing products, custom-molded products, and rubber-to-metal bonded products for various applications such as automotive, construction, and off-highway.</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';">Over the last three decades, ZONG YIH has built a remarkable reputation for its creativity and&nbsp; quality. We believe that our tremendous and continual growth stems from our promise to deliver&nbsp; only high-quality and high-reliability products with affordable pricing. ZONG YIH believes that&nbsp; this is the best way of advancing in global markets.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: 'Lucida Grande';">&nbsp;</span></p>
